values:
I haven't posted in this journal for a long time. I'm sorry :) I have been reading my friends page but to be honest the main reason I haven't updated here is because I've been wanting to change.

So I've created a new journal: <lj user= "kissclean">

I never thought I'd create a new journal. I've had this one for nearly 6 years and I've made so many wonderful friends. But I just feel like I've grown and changed and could do with a fresh start. I'm still the same person but I have different things to say and want to be able to use my journal differently. <lj user= "kissclean"> will be full of posts about fandom, crushes, my daily life, beauty and food ♥ All the things that I love :)

So, I'll be adding all you guys on my journal. If you feel like you don't want to come with me thats absolutely fine :) Just leave a comment below and I won't add you :)
